maintext:
Upcoming Reedsburg-Waunakee girls volleyball match will go toward disaster relief
The Reedsburg-Waunakee girls varsity volleyball match on Tuesday night (Sept. 11) will aid flood victims in the Reedsburg area.
There will be no admission charge. Donations will be accepted for the Sauk County disaster relief fund, Waunakee girls volleyball coach Anne Denkert said Thursday night.
The Badger North Conference match is scheduled to begin at 6 p.m. at Waunakee. The match was rescheduled from Aug. 30.
